I was going through a lot of pain and discomfort with my missing teeth, until a family friend of recommended SmileCURE Dental Clinic. Dr PRANAY & his team were very friendly since the start and made sure I was comfortable during the entire process. He explained the existing issues very well in simple terms and also the possible next steps towards resolving it. The entire team is the best qualified, friendly and hard working doctors

survey_response.review_text: I came here almost a year back for my dental treatment and I couldn’t be more satisfied with my results. This is by far one of the most organized and well managed services I have ever experienced. The Clinic is located near kadubeesenhalli Circle, which makes it really convenient. It is so well managed, that it hardly feels like you are visiting your Dentist, but instead a High End clinic with portable xray .and you know you’re in really good hands).The best part is that you always get a reminder text and an email a day prior to your visit to confirm the appointment, and a call on the day of the visit to ensure there are no delays from either sides. All of the equipment used for the dental procedures are well sanitized. The Doctors here are extremely polite and very well experienced and are more than happy to help you. They even provide a kit and a demo when you get your braces, and assist you throughout the whole journey wherever necessary. The only negative part about the whole experience was the traffic on the link road post 6:30pm. But overall it was worth it. It doesn’t matter if you are a teen, or a working individual, if Quality and Value for price is what you’re looking for, then I’d strongly recommend this place.
